{"members":[{"header_text":" روي:","body_text":"انّه لمّا نزلت <quranic_text>«وَ الْمُطَلَّقٰاتُ يَتَرَبَّصْنَ بِاَنْفُسِهِنَّ ثَلاٰثَةَ قُرُوءٍ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[البقرة۲۲۸]</footnote> قيل فما عدّة اللائي لم يحضن فنزلت <quranic_text>«وَ اللاّٰئِي لَمْ يَحِضْنَ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[الطلاق۴]</footnote> .","translation":"","aligned_body":"انّه لمّا نزلت TAG_OPEN:quranic_text وَ الْمُطَلَّقٰاتُ يَتَرَبَّصْنَ بِاَنْفُسِهِنَّ ثَلاٰثَةَ قُرُوءٍ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote البقرة ۲۲۸ TAG_CLOSE:footnote قيل فما عدّة اللائي لم يحضن فنزلت TAG_OPEN:quranic_text وَ اللاّٰئِي لَمْ يَحِضْنَ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote الطلاق ۴ TAG_CLOSE:footnote"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"انه","display":"انّه"},{"kind":"word","token":"لما","display":"لمّا"},{"kind":"word","token":"نزلت","display":"نزلت"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"المطلقات","display":"الْمُطَلَّقٰاتُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"يتربصن","display":"يَتَرَبَّصْنَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"بانفسهن","display":"بِاَنْفُسِهِنَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ثلاثه","display":"ثَلاٰثَةَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قروء","display":"قُرُوءٍ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"البقره","display":"البقرة"},{"kind":"word","token":"۲۲۸","display":"۲۲۸"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"قيل","display":"قيل"},{"kind":"word","token":"فما","display":"فما"},{"kind":"word","token":"عده","display":"عدّة"},{"kind":"word","token":"اللائي","display":"اللائي"},{"kind":"word","token":"لم","display":"لم"},{"kind":"word","token":"يحضن","display":"يحضن"},{"kind":"word","token":"فنزلت","display":"فنزلت"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"اللائي","display":"اللاّٰئِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"لم","display":"لَمْ"},{"kind":"word","to